history.content:
The application to Introduction to Mathematical Thinking, a 2-unit DeCal that aims to develop mathematical maturity and prepare students for courses like CS 70, is now live! http://apply.imt-decal.org


Class is on Tuesdays and Thursdays from 3:30-5:00PM. We cover topics such as propositional logic, proof techniques, modular arithmetic and counting. More details are available on our website, http://imt-decal.org. 


The application deadline is January 23rd, at 11:59PM. Apply at http://apply.imt-decal.org. Feel free to email us at imt-decal@berkeley.edu if you have any questions!
